headline: GE Aerospace Contracts And Partnerships Put Valuation Expectations In Focus
summary: GE Aerospace, part of General Electric (NYSE:GE), is working with Kratos Defense on the U.S. Air Force GEK1500 engine program for unmanned aerial systems. GE is supporting Starfighters Space on its STARLAUNCH I program, which recently reached a program milestone using GE Aerospace propulsion expertise. These contracts and partnerships expand GE's role across defense and emerging space platforms, focusing on next generation propulsion systems. For you as an investor following NYSE:GE, these...
